ActCanadian Race Relations Foundation Act
PrecisAppointment of MOSES GASHIRABAKE of Côte-Saint-Luc, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Race Relations Foundation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, on a part-time basis, effective May 28, 2018.
